{"tid":2030590,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"英國政黨 tweet  BNO 聯署呀 ~~","createTime":"2020-05-23T00:18:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T17:40:46.000Z","uid":89160,"like":36,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"c2f2c03c0798c9502aaae7d8f742ac16d6685c04","tid":2030590,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T00:18:21.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">呢個聯署係 Liberal Democrats Overseas 既 twitter 都有推<br />\nHong Kong Bill 提案人 Alistair Carmichael MP 就係 Liberal Democrats，佢地都需要做勢</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fuk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CIMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=7e8a3266\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e00659502beb6000e446c6be34f6979bc230f169","tid":2030590,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T00:19:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fuk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CIMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=7e8a3266\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong</a>"},{"pid":"9eacb5191dec22c70324abd0fa9c1dcebed48ab5","tid":2030590,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T00:21:07.000Z","msg":"英澳加聯合聲明：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/news/joint-statement-from-the-uk-australia-and-canada-on-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fnews%2Fjoint-statement-from-the-uk-australia-and-canada-on-hong-kong&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CIMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=b7dd2bce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/government/news/joint-statement-from-the-uk-australia-and-canada-on-hong-kong</a><br />\n<br />\nWe are deeply concerned at proposals for introducing legislation related to national security in Hong Kong.<br />\n<br />\nThe legally binding Joint Declaration, signed by China and the UK, sets out that Hong Kong will have a high degree of autonomy. It also provides that rights and freedoms, including those of the person, of the press, of assembly, of association and others, will be ensured by law in Hong Kong, and that the provisions of the two UN covenants on human rights (the International Covenant on Civil and Political Rights and International Covenant on Economic, Social and Cultural Rights) shall remain in force.<br />\n<br />\nMaking such a law on Hong Kong&rsquo;s behalf without the direct participation of its people, legislature or judiciary would clearly undermine the principle of &lsquo;One Country, Two Systems"},{"pid":"5197a834c22839c488b68120d939c36983ad414d","tid":2030590,"uid":195334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T00:21:32.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffae306746d4dea42af995696dca5e33031e0dc8","tid":2030590,"uid":46534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T00:25:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e8c9aa3985d3c36d544c9266279d15278e7a31aa","tid":2030590,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T00:28:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b2a4f54691ef33b8f032a4357a1c7eedaf09703","tid":2030590,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislik